Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's been five hundred years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.69,0:00:33.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Seven months, and twenty days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The time and seasons weather me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Like the moss upon my mane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And when I watch the sun come up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.31,0:00:44.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And it bathes me in its rays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:47.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It strikes me cold within my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.31,0:00:50.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,To remember I'm this way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:54.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I remember long before things
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:56.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Got to be so wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:00:59.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Those who spoke their minds did so
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:01.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With laughter and with song
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:04.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then one day I crossed the line
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.19,0:01:07.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And dared stand up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:10.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The last thing that I ever did
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:13.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And so your garden grew
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now I bake beneath the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I freeze beneath the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.88,0:01:21.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Patiently I bide my time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the decades come and go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still with each dawn and brand new sun
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:30.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I hope today's the day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.56,0:01:35.19,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That forgiveness finds its way to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And you let me fly away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I and everyone you see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:49.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Who decorate your path
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:52.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are only those whose guilt and crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Are measured by your wrath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.63,0:01:58.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I watch you as you pass by me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Eyes cast upon the ground
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:03.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your head bowed low in silent shame
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.44,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Weighed down by golden crown
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.13,0:02:09.25,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your highness I bow to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:12.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not by choice or own accord
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:15.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Forever with my nose against
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.69,0:02:17.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The plinth where I am stored
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:21.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yet there is no hate within my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.31,0:02:23.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I no longer need atone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.44,0:02:26.75,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I pity you, the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.06,0:02:29.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,With a heart made out of stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still I bake beneath the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.00,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And I freeze beneath the snow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.94,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Patiently I bide my time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.50,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,As the decades come and go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Still with each dawn~ and brand new sun
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:46.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I hope today's the day
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.69,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That forgiveness finds its way to you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.00,0:02:53.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And you let me fly away